namespace = DG_Catholics
namespace = DG_HeresySpread
country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.001
	title = "DG_Catholics.001.title"
	desc = "DG_Catholics.001.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	major = yes
	fire_only_once = yes
	trigger = { 
		is_religion_enabled = protestant
		religion_years = { 
			protestant = 50
		}
		tag = PAP
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		years = 10
	}
	immediate = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_global_flag = DG_Counter_Reformation
			random_list = { 
				10 = { 
					set_global_flag = DG_Small_Counterref
					log = "DG:[GetYear]:2530:Counter_Reformation:Birth:Rome:[This.GetName]:Small Counterreformation"
				}
				80 = { 
					set_global_flag = DG_Mild_Counterref
					log = "DG:[GetYear]:2530:Counter_Reformation:Birth:Rome:[This.GetName]:Mild Counterreformation"
				}
				10 = { 
					set_global_flag = DG_Large_Counterref
					log = "DG:[GetYear]:2530:Counter_Reformation:Birth:Rome:[This.GetName]:Large Counterreformation"
				}
			}
		}
		set_country_flag = DG_Catholic_Revival
	}
	option = { 
		name = "DG_Catholics.001.opta"
		hidden_effect = { 
			random_known_country = { 
				limit = { 
					religion = catholic
					NOT = { 
						has_country_flag = DG_Catholic_Revival
					}
					NOT = { 
						has_country_flag = DG_Religious_Compromise
					}
				}
				country_event = { 
					id = DG_Catholics.002
					days = 45
					random = 15
				}
			}
		}
	}
}

country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.003
	title = "DG_Catholics.003.title"
	desc = "DG_Catholics.003.desc"
	picture = RELIGIOUS_WARS_eventPicture
	is_triggered_only = yes
	fire_only_once = yes
	option = { 
		log = "DG:[GetYear]:[Root.GetName]:as Hussite, converted to Catholicism during counter-reformation:DG_Catholics.003"
		name = "DG_Catholics.003.opta"
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 90
		}
		change_religion = catholic
		force_converted = yes
	}
	option = { 
		name = "DG_Catholics.003.optb"
		log = "DG:[GetYear]:[Root.GetName]:as Hussite, converted to Lutheranism during counter-reformation:DG_Catholics.003"
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 10
		}
		change_religion = protestant
		force_converted = yes
	}
	option = { 
		name = "DG_Catholics.003.optc"
		log = "DG:[GetYear]:[Root.GetName]:stayed Hussite during counter-reformation:DG_Catholics.003"
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 0
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					stability = 3
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = ahf
					value = 1200
				}
			}
			else = { 
				add_stability = 1
			}
		}
		tooltip = { 
			add_stability = 1
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				is_emperor_of_china = yes
			}
			add_mandate = 5
		}
	}
}
country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.009
	title = "AI_Event"
	desc = "AI_Event"
	picture = all_church_state
	hidden = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes
	trigger = { 
		NOT = { 
			is_religion_enabled = reformed
		}
		OR = { 
			religion = catholic
			religion = avignonist
		}
		OR = { 
			tag = PAP
			tag = AVI
			is_emperor = yes
			is_papal_controller = yes
			AND = { 
				owns = 183
				OR = { 
					has_country_modifier = title_5
					has_country_modifier = title_6
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "AI_Event"
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_global_flag = DG_Burn_Jan_Hus
			}
			log = "DG - [Root.GetName] adds reform desire - After Hus Burn"
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					OR = { 
						tag = PAP
						tag = AVI
					}
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = kni
								value = 1
							}
						}
					}
					PAP = { 
						add_reform_desire = 0.0041
					}
				}
				if = { 
					limit = {

						}

						add_reform_desire = 0.0041
					}

							is_variable_equal = {

							}
						}

					PAP = {

							}
						}

			}

					limit = {

					}
				}

country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.010
	title = DG_Catholics.010.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.010.desc
	picture = catholic_order_founded
	fire_only_once = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes
	major = yes
	trigger = { 
		is_religion_enabled = reformed
		tag = PAP
		NOT = { 
			has_country_flag = Conclave_Underway
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_country_flag = jesuits_founded
		}
		has_global_flag = ignacio_de_loyola
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.010.opta
		add_devotion = 10
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_owned_province = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asx
							value = 0.001
						}
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = ata
					value = 10
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = atb
					value = 10
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = ata
								value = 100.001
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 100
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 0
								}
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 0
					}
				}
				set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_10
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_country_flag = jesuits_founded
			change_variable = { 
				which = jesuit_support
				value = 2
			}
		}
	}
}

		}

	}

			FROM = { 
				NOT = { 
					owned_by = PAP
				}
				owner = { 
					NOT = { 
						religion = catholic
					}
				}
			}
		}
		desc = "DG_Catholics.081.des3"

	picture = catholic_burning_church

		}
		FROM = { 
			province_id = 2530
		}
	}

		set_country_flag = urbs_mundi_captured
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				FROM = { 
					owned_by = PAP
				}

			hidden_effect = { 
				PAP = { 
					reverse_add_opinion = { 
						who = ROOT
						modifier = urbs_mundi_pope
					}
				}
				every_known_country = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							tag = PAP
						}
						religion = catholic
					}
					reverse_add_opinion = { 
						who = ROOT
						modifier = urbs_mundi_catholic
					}
				}
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				FROM = { 
					owner = { 
						NOT = { 
							religion = catholic
						}
					}
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = urbs_mundi_opinion_good_tt
			hidden_effect = { 
				every_known_country = { 
					limit = { 
						religion = catholic
					}
					reverse_add_opinion = { 
						who = ROOT
						modifier = urbs_mundi_good
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.DULYNOTED2"
	}
}
country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.082
	title = "AI_Event"
	desc = "AI_Event"
	picture = ai_only
	hidden = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = "AI_Event"
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				religion = catholic
				NOT = { 
					tag = PAP
				}
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					PAP = { 
						has_country_flag = Holds_Urbs_Mundi
					}
				}
				country_event = { 
					id = DG_Catholics.083
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					any_country = { 
						has_country_flag = Holds_Urbs_Mundi
						religion = catholic
					}
				}
				country_event = { 
					id = DG_Catholics.085
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					any_country = { 
						has_country_flag = Holds_Urbs_Mundi
						NOT = { 
							religion = catholic
						}
					}
				}
				country_event = { 
					id = DG_Catholics.087
				}
			}
		}
		else = { 
			every_country = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = Holds_Urbs_Mundi
				}
				clr_country_flag = Holds_Urbs_Mundi
			}
			set_country_flag = Holds_Urbs_Mundi
		}
	}
}
country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.083
	title = "DG_Catholics.083.title"
	desc = "DG_Catholics.083.desc"
	picture = catholic_excommunication
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = "DG_Catholics.083.opta"
		log = "DG:[GetYear]:[Root.GetName]:after conquest, refused to give Rome back to [PAP.GetName]:DG_Catholics.083"
		log = "DG:[GetYear]:[Root.GetName]:was excommunicated:DG_Catholics.083"
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				religion = catholic
			}
			excommunicate = ROOT
			add_papal_influence = -200
		}
		2530 = { 
			add_permanent_claim = PAP
		}
		PAP = { 
			clr_country_flag = Holds_Urbs_Mundi
		}
		set_country_flag = Holds_Urbs_Mundi
		custom_tooltip = urbs_mundi_opinion_held_tt
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_known_country = { 
				limit = { 
					religion = catholic
					OR = { 
						government = theocracy
						patriarch_authority = 0.75
					}
				}
				reverse_add_opinion = { 
					who = ROOT
					modifier = urbs_mundi_unlawful_strong
				}
			}
			every_known_country = { 
				limit = { 
					religion = catholic
					NOT = { 
						government = theocracy
					}
					NOT = { 
						patriarch_authority = 0.75
					}
				}
				reverse_add_opinion = { 
					who = ROOT
					modifier = urbs_mundi_unlawful_weak
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "DG_Catholics.083.optb"
		log = "DG:[GetYear]:[Root.GetName]:after conquest, gave Rome back to [PAP.GetName]:DG_Catholics.083"
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					exists = PAP
				}
			}
			PAP = { 
				clr_country_flag = POP_Init
			}
		}
		2530 = { 
			add_core = PAP
			cede_province = PAP
		}
		custom_tooltip = urbs_mundi_opinion_good_tt
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_known_country = { 
				limit = { 
					religion = catholic
				}
				reverse_add_opinion = { 
					who = ROOT
					modifier = urbs_mundi_good
				}
			}
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			PAP = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = Init.1
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							religion = catholic
						}
					}
					change_religion = catholic
				}
				add_government_reform = Pol_Mediumship4
				add_government_reform = Pol_Organisation3
				add_government_reform = Pol_Nobility1
				add_government_reform = Pol_Assembly1
			}
		}
	}
}

		name = "DG_Catholics.093.opta"
		log = "DG:[GetYear]:[Root.GetName]:refused concordat:DG_Catholics.093"
		log = "DG:[GetYear]:[Root.GetName]:was excommunicated:DG_Catholics.093"
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				religion = catholic
			}
			excommunicate = ROOT
			add_papal_influence = -200
		}
		2530 = { 
			add_permanent_claim = PAP
		}
		custom_tooltip = urbs_mundi_opinion_held_tt
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_known_country = { 
				limit = { 
					religion = catholic
					OR = { 
						government = theocracy
						patriarch_authority = 0.75
					}
				}
				reverse_add_opinion = { 
					who = ROOT
					modifier = urbs_mundi_unlawful_strong
				}
			}
			every_known_country = { 
				limit = { 
					religion = catholic
					NOT = { 
						government = theocracy
					}
					NOT = { 
						patriarch_authority = 0.75
					}
				}
				reverse_add_opinion = { 
					who = ROOT
					modifier = urbs_mundi_unlawful_weak
				}
			}
		}
		PAP = { 
			country_event = { 
				id = DG_Catholics.092
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "DG_Catholics.093.optb"
		add_treasury = -500
		log = "DG:[GetYear]:[Root.GetName]:accepted concordat:DG_Catholics.093"
		PAP = { 
			add_treasury = 500
			country_event = { 
				id = DG_Catholics.094
			}
		}
		add_papal_influence = -200
		set_country_flag = Concordat_of_Rome
	}
	option = { 
		name = "DG_Catholics.093.optc"
		log = "DG:[GetYear]:[Root.GetName]:instead of signing concordat, gave Rome back to [PAP.GetName]:DG_Catholics.093"
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					exists = PAP
				}
			}
			PAP = { 
				clr_country_flag = POP_Init
			}
		}
		2530 = { 
			add_core = PAP
			cede_province = PAP
		}
		custom_tooltip = urbs_mundi_opinion_good_tt
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_known_country = { 
				limit = { 
					religion = catholic
				}
				reverse_add_opinion = { 
					who = ROOT
					modifier = urbs_mundi_good
				}
			}
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			PAP = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = Init.1
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							religion = catholic
						}
					}
					change_religion = catholic
				}
				add_government_reform = Pol_Mediumship4
				add_government_reform = Pol_Organisation3
				add_government_reform = Pol_Nobility1
				add_government_reform = Pol_Assembly1
			}
		}
	}
}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.102
	title = "DG_Catholics.101.title"
	desc = "AI_Event"
	picture = all_church_state
	hidden = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes
	immediate = { 
		log = "DG:[GetYear]:[This.aab.GetValue]:Catholicism:Spread:[This.GetName]:[This.Owner.GetName]"
	}
	option = { 
		name = "EVT_AI"
		hidden_effect = { 
			random_list = { 
				10 = { 
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							OR = { 
								AND = { 
									is_variable_equal = { 
										which = adv
										value = 2
									}
								}
								AND = { 
									is_variable_equal = { 
										which = adx
										value = 2
									}
								}
								AND = { 
									is_variable_equal = { 
										which = adz
										value = 2
									}
								}
								AND = { 
									is_variable_equal = { 
										which = aeb
										value = 2
									}
								}
								AND = { 
									is_variable_equal = { 
										which = aed
										value = 2
									}
								}
								AND = { 
									is_variable_equal = { 
										which = aef
										value = 2
									}
								}
							}
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								NOT = { 
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = adv
											value = 1
										}
									}
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = adx
											value = 1
										}
									}
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = adz
											value = 1
										}
									}
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = aeb
											value = 1
										}
									}
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = aed
											value = 1
										}
									}
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = aef
											value = 1
										}
									}
								}
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = qae
								value = 1
							}
							province_event = { 
								id = DG_Convert.903
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = qae
								value = 0
							}
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									is_variable_equal = { 
										which = aaw
										value = 0
									}
								}
							}

								which = awp
								value = 0
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = aws
								value = 0
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = awv
								value = 0
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = awy
								value = 0
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = axb
								value = 0
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = axe
								value = 0
							}
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									is_variable_equal = {

									}
								}
							}
							set_variable = {

								}
							}
							set_variable = {

							}

						}

							which = ked

									set_variable = { 
										which = aen
										value = 0
									}
								}
								else = { 
									divide_variable = { 
										which = aen
										which = aaw
									}
								}
								if = { 
									limit = { 
										OR = { 
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aax
													value = 0
												}
											}
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aeo
													value = 0.001
												}
											}
										}
									}
									set_variable = { 
										which = aeo
										value = 0
									}
								}
								else = { 
									divide_variable = { 
										which = aeo
										which = aax
									}
								}
								if = { 
									limit = { 
										OR = { 
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aay
													value = 0
												}
											}
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aec
													value = 0.001
												}
											}
										}
									}
									set_variable = { 
										which = aec
										value = 0
									}
								}
								else = { 
									divide_variable = { 
										which = aec
										which = aay
									}
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = axq
									which = aen
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = axr
									which = aeo
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = axs
									which = aec
								}
								multiply_variable = { 
									which = axq
									value = 100
								}
								multiply_variable = { 
									which = axr
									value = 100
								}
								multiply_variable = { 
									which = axs
									value = 100
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = ayo
									which = awy
								}
								change_variable = { 
									which = ayo
									which = awz
								}
								change_variable = { 
									which = ayo
									which = axa
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = ayu
									which = ayo
								}
								if = { 
									limit = { 
										AND = { 
											check_variable = { 
												which = ayu
												value = 0.001
											}
										}
									}
									divide_variable = { 
										which = ayu
										which = aaz
									}
									multiply_variable = { 
										which = ayu
										value = 100
									}
								}
							}
							else_if = { 
								limit = { 
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = aed
											value = 1
										}
									}
								}
								change_variable = { 
									which = axb
									which = kdu
								}
								change_variable = { 
									which = axc
									which = kdv
								}
								change_variable = { 
									which = axd
									which = kdw
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = aep
									which = axb
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = aeq
									which = axc
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = aee
									which = axd
								}
								if = { 
									limit = { 
										OR = { 
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aaw
													value = 0
												}
											}
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aep
													value = 0.001
												}
											}
										}
									}
									set_variable = { 
										which = aep
										value = 0
									}
								}
								else = { 
									divide_variable = { 
										which = aep
										which = aaw
									}
								}
								if = { 
									limit = { 
										OR = { 
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aax
													value = 0
												}
											}
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aeq
													value = 0.001
												}
											}
										}
									}
									set_variable = { 
										which = aeq
										value = 0
									}
								}
								else = { 
									divide_variable = { 
										which = aeq
										which = aax
									}
								}
								if = { 
									limit = { 
										OR = { 
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aay
													value = 0
												}
											}
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aee
													value = 0.001
												}
											}
										}
									}
									set_variable = { 
										which = aee
										value = 0
									}
								}
								else = { 
									divide_variable = { 
										which = aee
										which = aay
									}
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = axt
									which = aep
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = axu
									which = aeq
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = axv
									which = aee
								}
								multiply_variable = { 
									which = axt
									value = 100
								}
								multiply_variable = { 
									which = axu
									value = 100
								}
								multiply_variable = { 
									which = axv
									value = 100
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = ayp
									which = axb
								}
								change_variable = { 
									which = ayp
									which = axc
								}
								change_variable = { 
									which = ayp
									which = axd
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = ayv
									which = ayp
								}
								if = { 
									limit = { 
										AND = { 
											check_variable = { 
												which = ayv
												value = 0.001
											}
										}
									}
									divide_variable = { 
										which = ayv
										which = aaz
									}
									multiply_variable = { 
										which = ayv
										value = 100
									}
								}
							}
							else_if = { 
								limit = { 
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = aef
											value = 1
										}
									}
								}
								change_variable = { 
									which = axe
									which = kdu
								}
								change_variable = { 
									which = axf
									which = kdv
								}
								change_variable = { 
									which = axg
									which = kdw
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = aer
									which = axe
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = aes
									which = axf
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = aeg
									which = axg
								}
								if = { 
									limit = { 
										OR = { 
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aaw
													value = 0
												}
											}
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aer
													value = 0.001
												}
											}
										}
									}
									set_variable = { 
										which = aer
										value = 0
									}
								}
								else = { 
									divide_variable = { 
										which = aer
										which = aaw
									}
								}
								if = { 
									limit = { 
										OR = { 
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aax
													value = 0
												}
											}
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aes
													value = 0.001
												}
											}
										}
									}
									set_variable = { 
										which = aes
										value = 0
									}
								}
								else = { 
									divide_variable = { 
										which = aes
										which = aax
									}
								}
								if = { 
									limit = { 
										OR = { 
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aay
													value = 0
												}
											}
											AND = { 
												is_variable_equal = { 
													which = aeg
													value = 0.001
												}
											}
										}
									}

										value = 0
									}
								}
								else = {

										which = aeg
										which = aay
									}
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = axw
									which = aer
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = axx
									which = aes
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = axy
									which = aeg
								}
								multiply_variable = { 
									which = axw
									value = 100
								}
								multiply_variable = { 
									which = axx
									value = 100
								}
								multiply_variable = { 
									which = axy
									value = 100
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = ayq
									which = axe
								}
								change_variable = { 
									which = ayq
									which = axf
								}
								change_variable = { 
									which = ayq
									which = axg
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = ayw
									which = ayq
								}
								if = { 
									limit = { 
										AND = { 
											check_variable = { 
												which = ayw
												value = 0.001
											}
										}
									}
									divide_variable = { 
										which = ayw
										which = aaz
									}
									multiply_variable = { 
										which = ayw
										value = 100
									}
								}
							}
							set_province_flag = DG_Update
							set_variable = { 
								which = kdu
								value = 0
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = kdv
								value = 0
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = kdw
								value = 0
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = qac
						value = 0
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}
}
province_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.118
	title = "DG_Catholics.118.title"
	desc = "DG_Catholics.118.desc"
	picture = ANGLICAN_SERMON_eventPicture
	trigger = { 
		has_global_flag = DG_Counter_Reformation
		is_religion_enabled = reformed
		has_province_flag = printing_press_p
		owner = { 
			reform_desire = 1.00
		}
		NOT = { 
			had_global_flag = { 
				flag = DG_Counter_Reformation
				days = 18250
			}
		}
		AND = { 
			continent = europe
			religion = catholic
			NOT = { 
				province_id = 2530
			}
			is_reformation_center = no
			is_island = no
			expelling_minorities = no
			development = 10
			NOT = { 
				Academia = 100
			}
			NOT = { 
				current_age = age_of_revolutions
			}
			NOT = { 
				calc_true_if = { 
					all_province = { 
						continent = europe
						religion = ROOT
						is_reformation_center = yes
					}
					amount = 3
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				any_neighbor_province = { 
					is_reformation_center = yes
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				any_province = { 
					superregion = PREV
					is_reformation_center = yes
					religion = catholic
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_climate = tropical
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_climate = arid
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_climate = arctic
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_terrain = arctic
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_terrain = taiga
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_terrain = tundra
			}
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		years = 20
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.50
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = DG_Catholic_Revival
			}
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.50
			province_id = 2530
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.75
			is_capital = yes
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.90
			superregion = france_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.50
			superregion = italy_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.50
			superregion = iberia_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 1.50
			superregion = germany_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.75
			superregion = greater_austrian_circle_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 1.25
			superregion = balkan_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.95
			superregion = commonwealth_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 1.50
			superregion = scandinavian_superregion
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 5.0
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = accept_01
			}
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 10.0
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = silence_01
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.GOOD"
		trigger = { 
			owner = { 
				religion = catholic
			}
		}
		add_reform_center = catholic
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_province_modifier = religious_enthusiasm
			}
			extend_province_modifier = { 
				name = religious_enthusiasm
				duration = 3650
			}
		}
		else = { 
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = religious_enthusiasm
				duration = 3650
				hidden = yes
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.DAMN"
		trigger = { 
			owner = { 
				NOT = { 
					religion = catholic
				}
			}
		}
		add_reform_center = catholic
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_province_modifier = heretic_centre
			}
			extend_province_modifier = { 
				name = heretic_centre
				duration = 3650
			}
		}
		else = { 
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = heretic_centre
				duration = 3650
				hidden = yes
			}
		}
	}
}

	}

										value = 0.1
									}
								}

								which = amn
								value = 0.1
							}
							add_devastation = 0.1

							which = amn
							value = 0

						set_variable = { 
							which = kdt
							value = 0

							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = { 
									which = aef
									value = 1
								}
							}
						}

							which = ayw
						}

							value = 0.90
						}
						divide_variable = {

							value = 10
						}

									}
								}

							subtract_variable = {

									check_variable = { 
										which = ayt
										value = 80

								}

								AND = {

									}

						limit = {

						}

							name = MN_max_U.16
							duration = 365
						}
					}
					else = { 
						add_province_modifier = { 
							name = MN_max_U.16
							duration = 365
							hidden = yes
						}
					}

						limit = { 
							owner = { 
								has_country_flag = cat_unrest_info
							}
						}
						set_province_flag = mn_unrest_max_1
					}
				}
			}
			10 = { 
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						OR = { 
							AND = { 
								AND = { 
									is_variable_equal = { 
										which = adv
										value = 1

	id = DG_Catholics.312

	is_triggered_only = yes

		name = "OPT.OHNO"

				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_mid_1_tt

			mn_unrest_mid_5 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_mid_2_tt

				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_imp_3_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_max_1 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_max_1_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_max_5 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_max_2_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_max_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_max_3_tt

		}
	}
	after = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_min_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_min_5

			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_low_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_low_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_low_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_mid_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_mid_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_mid_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_imp_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_imp_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_imp_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_max_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_max_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_max_10
		}
	}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.401
	title = DG_Catholics.401.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.401.desc
	picture = catholic_monks
	trigger = { 
		owner = { 
			OR = { 
				religion = catholic
				religion = avignonist
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = bbo
					value = -1
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_institution = Academia
			}
		}
		OR = { 
			AND = { 
				NOT = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = aax
							value = 10
						}
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = abx
						value = 0.750
					}
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				check_variable = { 
					which = aax
					value = 5
				}
			}
		}
		has_owner_culture = yes
		has_owner_religion = yes
		is_core = owner
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = augustinian_order
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = dominican_order
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = cistercian_order
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = franciscan_order
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = jesuit_order
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		years = 200
		modifier = { 
			factor = 1.2
			owner = { 
				reform_desire = 0.25
			}
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 1.2
			owner = { 
				reform_desire = 0.5
			}
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 1.2
			owner = { 
				reform_desire = 0.75
			}
		}

			factor = 1.2

				reform_desire = 1.0
			}
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 1.5
			is_religion_enabled = protestant
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 1.5
			owner = { 
				has_institution = Scientific_Method
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.401.opta
		trigger = { 
			AND = { 
				NOT = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = aax
							value = 10
						}
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = abx
						value = 0.750
					}
				}
			}
		}

			factor = 15
		}

			add_treasury = -20
			hidden_effect = { 
				every_owned_province = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = asx
								value = 0.001
							}
						}
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 5
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = atb
						value = 5
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 100.001
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 100
						}
					}

									}
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 0
						}
					}
					set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_5
		}
		add_province_modifier = { 
			name = augustinian_order
			duration = 18250
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			change_variable = { 
				which = aan
				value = 20
			}
			if = {

						value = 5

					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 100.001
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							NOT = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = ata
										value = 0
									}
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 0
						}
					}
					set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_5
		}

			name = cistercian_order
			duration = 18250
		}

				set_variable = {

				}
			}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.402
	title = DG_Catholics.402.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.402.desc
	picture = catholic_monks
	is_triggered_only = yes
	trigger = { 
		has_province_modifier = augustinian_order
		owner = { 
			OR = { 
				religion = catholic
				religion = avignonist
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = bbo
					value = -1
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_institution = Academia
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.402.opta
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = arn
				value = 10
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					always = yes
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = atc
								value = 0.001
							}
						}
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ath
									value = 0.001
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = aro
							which = asx
						}
						change_variable = { 
							which = aro
							which = arn
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = aro
										which = ath
									}
								}
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = arn
								which = ath
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = arn
								which = asx
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = aro
							value = 0
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = asx
									value = 0.001
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = arn
							value = 0
						}
						subtract_variable = { 
							which = arn
							which = asx
						}
					}
				}
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = asx
				which = arn
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = asz
				which = arn
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = asx
				value = 0.1
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = asx
				value = 10
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = asz
				value = 0.1
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = asz
				value = 10
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asx
							value = 100
						}
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = asx
					value = 100
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = asx
								value = 0
							}
						}
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = asx
					value = 0
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = arn
				value = 0
			}
			set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
		}
		custom_tooltip = monastic_power_increase
	}
}

							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = asx
									value = 0.001
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = arn
							value = 0
						}
						subtract_variable = { 
							which = arn
							which = asx
						}
					}
				}
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = asx
				which = arn
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = asz
				which = arn
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = asx
				value = 0.1
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = asx
				value = 10
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = asz
				value = 0.1
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = asz
				value = 10
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asx
							value = 100
						}
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = asx
					value = 100
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = asx
								value = 0
							}
						}
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = asx
					value = 0
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = arn
				value = 0
			}
			set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
		}
		custom_tooltip = monastic_power_increase
		owner = { 
			add_faction_influence = { 
				faction = FC_CL
				influence = 5
			}
		}
	}

country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.407
	title = DG_Catholics.407.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.407.desc
	picture = catholic_monastic_town
	is_triggered_only = yes
	trigger = { 
		any_owned_province = { 
			OR = { 
				has_province_modifier = augustinian_order
				has_province_modifier = cistercian_order
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_province_modifier = rural_development_efforts
			}
		}
		OR = { 
			religion = catholic
			religion = avignonist
		}
		NOT = { 
			adm_tech = 35
		}
		is_at_war = no
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.407.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 60
			modifier = { 
				NOT = { 
					stability = 1
				}
				factor = 0.5
			}
			modifier = { 
				NOT = { 
					stability = 0
				}
				factor = 0.1
			}
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			change_variable = { 
				which = ahf
				value = -120
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = 1200
						}
					}
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						stability = 3
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 1200
					}
				}
				else = { 
					subtract_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 1200
					}
					add_stability = 1
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = ahf
								value = 0
							}
						}
					}
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							stability = -2
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 0
					}
				}
				else = { 
					change_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 1200
					}
					add_stability = -1
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				which = ahf
			}
			divide_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				value = 12
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				value = 0.1
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				value = 10
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = lsc
				value = 100
			}
			subtract_variable = { 
				which = lsc
				which = ahd
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = POP_StabSubtract10
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				is_emperor_of_china = yes
			}
			add_mandate = -0.5
		}
		random_owned_province = { 
			limit = { 
				OR = { 
					has_province_modifier = augustinian_order
					has_province_modifier = cistercian_order
				}
				NOT = { 
					has_province_modifier = rural_development_efforts
				}
			}
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = rural_development_efforts
				duration = 3650
			}
			custom_tooltip = rural_development_efforts_tt
			add_unrest = 5
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.407.optb
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 30
			modifier = { 
				NOT = { 
					treasury = 20
				}
				factor = 0.5
			}
			modifier = { 
				num_of_loans = 1
				factor = 0.5
			}
			modifier = { 
				is_bankrupt = yes
				factor = 0
			}
		}
		add_treasury = -20
		random_owned_province = { 
			limit = { 
				OR = { 
					has_province_modifier = augustinian_order
					has_province_modifier = cistercian_order
				}
				NOT = {

				}
			}
			add_province_modifier = {

	title = DG_Catholics.410.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.410.desc

		OR = { 
			num_of_owned_provinces_with = {

			}
			num_of_owned_provinces_with = { 
				value = 2

		name = DG_Catholics.410.optc
		trigger = { 
			NOT = { 
				tag = PAP
			}
		}
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 25
		}
		add_prestige = -5
		add_papal_influence = -5
	}
	after = { 
		trigger_switch = { 
			on_trigger = has_country_flag
			franciscan_dispute = { 
				clr_country_flag = franciscan_dispute
			}
			cistercian_dispute = { 
				clr_country_flag = cistercian_dispute
			}
		}
	}
}

					value = 5

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.414
	title = DG_Catholics.414.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.414.desc
	picture = catholic_monks_preaching
	trigger = { 
		owner = { 
			religion = catholic
			NOT = { 
				has_country_modifier = religious_tolerance
			}
			NOT = { 
				is_excommunicated = yes
			}
			check_variable = { 
				which = jesuit_support
				value = 1
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_country_flag = jesuits_suppressed
			}
		}
		NOT = { 
			religion_years = { 
				protestant = 120
			}
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = jesuit_activity
		}
		OR = { 
			OR = { 
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adv
						value = 2
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adx
						value = 2
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adz
						value = 2
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = aeb
						value = 2
					}

country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.415
	title = DG_Catholics.415.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.415.desc
	picture = catholic_monks
	is_triggered_only = yes
	trigger = { 
		religion = catholic
		check_variable = { 
			which = jesuit_support
			value = 1
		}
		any_owned_province = { 
			has_province_modifier = jesuit_activity
		}
		is_at_war = no
		NOT = { 
			has_country_flag = dg_jesuit_education
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_country_flag = jesuits_suppressed
		}
		NOT = { 
			is_excommunicated = yes
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		days = 1
	}
	immediate = { 
		set_country_flag = dg_jesuit_education
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.415.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 50
		}
		capital_scope = { 
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = jesuit_college
				duration = 36500
			}
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_owned_province = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asx
							value = 0.001
						}
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = ata
					value = 10
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = atb
					value = 10
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = ata
								value = 100.001
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 100
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 0
								}
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 0
					}
				}
				set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_10
		hidden_effect = { 
			change_variable = { 
				which = jesuit_support
				value = 1
			}
			set_country_flag = jesuit_colleges
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.415.optb
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 30
			modifier = { 
				factor = 1.5
				NOT = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 30
						}
					}
				}
			}
		}
		add_country_modifier = { 
			name = jesuit_schools
			duration = -1
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_owned_province = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asx
							value = 0.001
						}
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = ata
					value = 20
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = atb
					value = 20
				}
				if = { 
					limit = {

							check_variable = { 
								which = ata
								value = 100.001
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = {

						value = 100
					}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.502
	title = DG_Catholics.502.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.502.desc
	picture = catholic_canonization
	is_triggered_only = yes
	immediate = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			owner = { 
				set_country_flag = national_saint
				clr_country_flag = sainthood_candidate
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.502.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 50
			modifier = { 
				owner = { 
					NOT = { 
						stability = -2
					}
				}
				factor = 1.4
			}
			modifier = { 
				owner = { 
					NOT = { 
						stability = -1
					}
				}
				factor = 1.4
			}
			modifier = { 
				owner = { 
					NOT = { 
						stability = 0
					}
				}
				factor = 1.4
			}
		}
		owner = { 
			add_prestige = 10
			add_opinion = { 
				who = PAP
				modifier = papacy_great
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						stability = 3
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 1200
					}
				}
				else = { 
					add_stability = 1
				}
			}
			tooltip = { 
				add_stability = 1
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					is_emperor_of_china = yes
				}
				add_mandate = 5
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.502.optb
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 50
			modifier = { 
				owner = { 
					stability = 1
				}
				factor = 1.4
			}
			modifier = { 
				owner = { 
					stability = 2
				}
				factor = 1.4
			}
			modifier = { 
				owner = { 
					stability = 3
				}
				factor = 1.4
			}
			modifier = { 
				owner = { 
					NOT = { 
						treasury = 25
					}
				}
				factor = 0.5
			}
			modifier = { 
				owner = { 
					num_of_loans = 1
				}
				factor = 0.5
			}
			modifier = { 
				owner = { 
					is_bankrupt = yes
				}
				factor = 0.1
			}
		}
		owner = { 
			add_treasury = -25
			hidden_effect = { 
				change_variable = { 
					which = ahf
					value = 600
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = ahf
								value = 1200
							}
						}
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							stability = 3
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = 1200
						}
					}
					else = { 
						subtract_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = 1200
						}
						add_stability = 1
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ahf
									value = 0
								}
							}
						}
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							NOT = { 
								stability = -2
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = 0
						}
					}
					else = { 
						change_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = 1200
						}
						add_stability = -1
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = ahd
					which = ahf
				}
				divide_variable = { 
					which = ahd
					value = 12
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = ahd
					value = 0.1
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = ahd
					value = 10
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = lsc
					value = 100
				}
				subtract_variable = { 
					which = lsc
					which = ahd
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = POP_StabAdd50
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					is_emperor_of_china = yes
				}
				add_mandate = 2.5
			}
		}
		add_province_modifier = { 
			name = catholic_pilgrimage
			duration = -1
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			change_variable = { 
				which = aan
				value = -25
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = aan
								value = 1.0
							}
						}
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = aan
					value = 1.0
				}
			}
			set_province_flag = POP_ChangedWealth
		}
	}
}

					which = ahf
				}
				divide_variable = { 
					which = ahd
					value = 12
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = ahd
					value = 0.1
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = ahd
					value = 10
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = lsc
					value = 100
				}
				subtract_variable = { 
					which = lsc
					which = ahd
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = POP_StabAdd50
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					is_emperor_of_china = yes
				}
				add_mandate = 2.5
			}
		}
		add_province_modifier = { 
			name = catholic_pilgrimage
			duration = -1
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			change_variable = { 
				which = aan
				value = -25
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = aan
								value = 1.0
							}
						}
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = aan
					value = 1.0
				}
			}
			set_province_flag = POP_ChangedWealth
		}
	}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.504
	title = DG_Catholics.504.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.504.desc
	picture = catholic_bishop
	is_triggered_only = yes
	trigger = { 
		OR = { 
			AND = { 
				owner = { 
					religion = catholic
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asx
							value = 30
						}
					}
				}
				PAP = { 
					NOT = { 
						has_ruler_flag = peasant_success
					}
					has_regency = no
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				owner = { 
					religion = avignonist
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asx
							value = 30
						}
					}
				}
				AVI = { 
					NOT = { 
						has_ruler_flag = peasant_success
					}
					has_regency = no
				}
			}
		}
		OR = { 
			OR = { 
				has_province_modifier = catholic_archbishopric
				has_province_modifier = preeminent_region_city
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = aax
						value = 10
					}
				}
			}
			OR = { 
				has_province_modifier = augustinian_order
				has_province_modifier = dominican_order
				has_province_modifier = cistercian_order
				has_province_modifier = franciscan_order
				has_province_modifier = jesuit_order
			}
			has_cardinal = yes
		}
		religion = catholic
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = greedy_bishop
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = absentee_bishop
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = indulgence_peddler
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = religious_scandal_province
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = peasant_success_story
		}
	}
	immediate = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					owner = { 
						religion = catholic
					}
				}
				PAP = { 
					set_ruler_flag = peasant_success
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					owner = { 
						religion = avignonist
					}
				}
				AVI = { 
					set_ruler_flag = peasant_success
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.504.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 25
			modifier = { 
				NOT = { 
					num_of_cardinals = 1
				}
				factor = 2
			}
		}
		add_province_modifier = { 
			name = peasant_success_story
			duration = 1825
		}
		owner = { 
			hidden_effect = { 
				change_variable = { 
					which = ahf
					value = 120
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = ahf
								value = 1200
							}
						}
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							stability = 3
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = 1200
						}
					}
					else = { 
						subtract_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = 1200
						}
						add_stability = 1
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ahf
									value = 0
								}
							}
						}
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							NOT = { 
								stability = -2
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = 0
						}
					}
					else = { 
						change_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = 1200
						}
						add_stability = -1
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = ahd
					which = ahf
				}
				divide_variable = { 
					which = ahd
					value = 12
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = ahd
					value = 0.1
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = ahd
					value = 10
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = lsc
					value = 100
				}
				subtract_variable = { 
					which = lsc
					which = ahd
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = POP_StabAdd10
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					is_emperor_of_china = yes
				}
				add_mandate = 0.5
			}
			add_opinion = { 
				who = PAP
				modifier = papacy_good
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.504.optb
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 25
			modifier = { 
				NOT = { 
					stability = 1
				}

			}
		}

			name = peasant_success_story
			duration = 3650
		}

					value = 300
				}

							}
						}

							stability = 3
						}

							which = ahf
							value = 1200
						}
					}
					else = { 
						subtract_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = 1200
						}
						add_stability = 1
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ahf
									value = 0
								}
							}
						}
					}

							NOT = { 
								stability = -2
							}

					}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.505
	title = DG_Catholics.505.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.505.desc
	picture = catholic_bishop
	is_triggered_only = yes
	trigger = { 
		owner = { 
			OR = { 
				religion = catholic
				religion = avignonist
			}
			NOT = { 
				tag = PAP
			}
			NOT = { 
				tag = AVI
			}
		}
		OR = { 
			has_province_modifier = preeminent_region_city
			AND = { 
				check_variable = { 
					which = aax
					value = 10
				}
			}
		}
		religion = owner
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = catholic_archbishopric
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = greedy_bishop
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = effective_bishop
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = absentee_bishop
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = indulgence_peddler
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = religious_scandal_province
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.505.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 70
		}
		add_province_modifier = { 
			name = effective_bishop
			duration = 7300
		}
		owner = { 
			hidden_effect = { 
				every_owned_province = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = asx
								value = 0.001
							}
						}
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 5
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = atb
						value = 5
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 100.001
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							NOT = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = ata
										value = 0
									}
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 0
						}
					}
					set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_5
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.505.optb
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 30
			modifier = { 
				owner = { 
					NOT = { 
						treasury = 25
					}
				}
				factor = 0.3
			}
			modifier = { 
				owner = { 
					num_of_loans = 1
				}
				factor = 0.3
			}
			modifier = { 
				owner = { 
					is_bankrupt = yes
				}
				factor = 0.1
			}
		}
		owner = { 
			add_treasury = -25
			hidden_effect = { 
				every_owned_province = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = asx
								value = 0.001
							}
						}
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 10
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = atb
						value = 10
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 100.001
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							NOT = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = ata
										value = 0
									}
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 0
						}
					}
					set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_10
		}
		add_province_modifier = { 
			name = effective_bishop
			duration = 7300
		}
		random_list = { 
			50 = { 
				owner = { 
					define_advisor = { 
						religion = catholic
						culture = ROOT
						type = theologian_CL
						discount = yes
					}
				}
			}
			50 = { 
				owner = { 
					define_advisor = { 
						religion = catholic
						culture = ROOT
						type = inquisitor_CL
						discount = yes
					}
				}
			}
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			change_variable = { 
				which = aan
				value = 25
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = aan
								value = 1.0
							}
						}
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = aan
					value = 1.0
				}
			}
			set_province_flag = POP_ChangedWealth
		}
	}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.506
	title = DG_Catholics.506.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.506.desc
	picture = catholic_bishop
	trigger = { 
		OR = { 
			AND = { 
				is_capital = yes
				owner = { 
					num_of_cities = 10
				}
			}
			has_province_modifier = effective_bishop
		}
		OR = { 
			has_province_modifier = preeminent_region_city
			AND = { 
				check_variable = { 
					which = aax
					value = 20
				}
			}
		}
		owner = { 
			AND = { 
				check_variable = { 
					which = asx
					value = 30
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				tag = PAP
			}
			NOT = { 
				tag = AVI
			}
			NOT = { 
				war_with = PAP
			}
			NOT = { 
				is_excommunicated = yes
			}
		}
		OR = { 
			is_capital = yes
			AND = { 
				superregion = italy_superregion
				has_owner_culture = yes
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = aax
						value = 25
					}
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				any_neighbor_province = { 
					any_neighbor_province = { 
						has_province_flag = catholic_archbishopric
					}
				}
			}
		}
		any_neighbor_province = { 
			owner = { 
				religion = catholic
			}
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = catholic_archbishopric
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = absentee_bishop
		}
		is_core = owner
		controlled_by = owner
		has_siege = no
		PAP = { 
			has_regency = no
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		years = 200
		modifier = { 
			OR = { 
				is_capital = yes
				has_province_modifier = effective_bishop
			}
			factor = 0.5
		}
		modifier = { 
			has_province_modifier = greedy_bishop
			factor = 2
		}
		modifier = { 
			owner = { 
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = asx
						value = 75
					}
				}
			}
			factor = 0.7
		}
		modifier = { 
			owner = { 
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = asx
						value = 50
					}
				}
			}
			factor = 0.7
		}
		modifier = { 
			owner = { 
				num_of_cardinals = 3
			}
			factor = 0.7
		}
		modifier = { 
			owner = { 
				num_of_cardinals = 6
			}
			factor = 0.7
		}
		modifier = { 
			owner = { 
				num_of_cardinals = 9
			}
			factor = 0.7
		}
		modifier = { 
			AND = { 
				NOT = { 
					religion = catholic
				}
				NOT = { 
					religion = avignonist
				}
			}
			factor = 1.4
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.506.opta
		add_province_modifier = { 
			name = catholic_archbishopric
			duration = -1
		}
		set_province_flag = catholic_archbishopric
		owner = { 
			add_papal_influence = 5
		}
	}
}
country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.507
	title = DG_Catholics.507.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.507.desc
	picture = catholic_papal_legate
	trigger = { 
		religion = catholic
		is_papal_controller = no
		NOT = { 
			any_neighbor_country = { 
				has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
			}
		}
		exists = PAP
		NOT = { 
			tag = PAP
		}
		AND = { 
			is_variable_equal = { 
				which = bbo
				value = -1
			}
		}
		is_excommunicated = no
		any_neighbor_country = { 
			religion = catholic
			is_papal_controller = no
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = bbo
					value = -1
				}
			}
			is_excommunicated = no
			ai = yes
			NOT = { 
				tag = PAP
			}
			NOT = { 
				war_with = ROOT
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_opinion = { 
					who = ROOT
					value = 50
				}
			}
			OR = { 
				is_rival = ROOT
				is_enemy = ROOT
			}
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		years = 300
		modifier = { 
			exists = AVI
			AVI = { 
				AND = { 
					government = theocracy
					has_reform = Pol_Mediumship4
				}
			}
			factor = 2
		}
		modifier = { 
			OR = { 
				AND = { 
					tag = POL
					is_rival = TEU
				}
				AND = { 
					tag = TEU
					is_rival = POL
				}
			}
			factor = 0.25
		}
	}
	immediate = { 
		random_neighbor_country = { 
			limit = { 
				religion = catholic
				is_papal_controller = no
				NOT = { 
					is_excommunicated = yes
				}
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = bbo
						value = -1
					}
				}
				ai = yes
				NOT = { 
					tag = PAP
				}
				NOT = { 
					war_with = ROOT
				}
				NOT = { 
					has_opinion = { 
						who = ROOT
						value = 50
					}
				}
				OR = { 
					is_rival = ROOT
					is_enemy = ROOT
				}
			}
			set_country_flag = aggrieved_party
			add_opinion = { 
				who = ROOT
				modifier = grievance
			}
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					any_neighbor_country = { 
						has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						truce_with = ROOT
					}
				}
				set_country_flag = grievance_military
				random_neighbor_country = { 
					limit = { 
						has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
					}
					set_country_flag = grievance_military
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					any_neighbor_country = { 
						has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						trade_embargo_by = ROOT
					}
				}
				set_country_flag = grievance_trade
				random_neighbor_country = { 
					limit = { 
						has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
					}
					set_country_flag = grievance_trade
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						has_country_flag = grievance_military
					}
					NOT = { 
						has_country_flag = grievance_trade
					}
				}
				set_country_flag = grievance_diplomatic
				random_neighbor_country = { 
					limit = { 
						has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
					}
					set_country_flag = grievance_diplomatic
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.507.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 25
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = grievance_military
			}
			add_mil_power = -100
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = grievance_trade
			}
			add_country_modifier = { 
				name = minor_trade_crisis
				duration = 2000
			}
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = grievance_diplomatic
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					monthly_income = 50
				}
				add_treasury = -200
				random_neighbor_country = { 
					limit = { 
						has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
					}
					add_treasury = 200
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					monthly_income = 25
				}
				add_treasury = -150
				random_neighbor_country = { 
					limit = { 
						has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
					}
					add_treasury = 150
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					monthly_income = 10
				}
				add_treasury = -100
				random_neighbor_country = { 
					limit = { 
						has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
					}
					add_treasury = 100
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					monthly_income = 5
				}
				add_treasury = -50
				random_neighbor_country = { 
					limit = { 
						has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
					}
					add_treasury = 50
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					monthly_income = 2
				}
				add_treasury = 25
				random_neighbor_country = { 
					limit = {
