country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.509
	title = DG_Catholics.509.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.509.desc
	picture = catholic_trial
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.509.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 50
		}
		add_prestige = 5
		every_country = { 
			limit = { 
				OR = { 
					AND = { 
						government = theocracy
						has_reform = Pol_Mediumship4
					}
					is_papal_controller = yes
				}
			}
			reverse_add_opinion = { 
				who = ROOT
				modifier = papacy_great
			}
		}
		random_neighbor_country = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
			}
			set_country_flag = lenient_ruling
			add_opinion = { 
				who = PAP
				modifier = papacy_bad
			}
			country_event = { 
				id = DG_Catholics.510
				days = 30
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.509.optb
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 50
		}
		every_country = { 
			limit = { 
				OR = { 
					AND = { 
						government = theocracy
						has_reform = Pol_Mediumship4
					}
					is_papal_controller = yes
				}
			}
			reverse_add_opinion = { 
				who = ROOT
				modifier = papacy_great
			}
		}
		random_neighbor_country = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
			}
			add_opinion = { 
				who = PAP
				modifier = papacy_bad
			}
			country_event = { 
				id = DG_Catholics.510
				days = 30
			}
		}
	}
	after = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = arbitration_bribe
				value = 0
			}
			clr_country_flag = grievance_diplomatic
			clr_country_flag = grievance_military
			clr_country_flag = grievance_trade
		}
	}
}
country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.510
	title = DG_Catholics.510.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.510.desc
	picture = catholic_trial
	is_triggered_only = yes
	immediate = { 
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				clr_country_flag = aggrieved_party
			}
			FROM = { 
				set_country_flag = aggrieved_party
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.510.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 50
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = grievance_military
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = lenient_ruling
				}
				add_mil_power = -100
			}
			else = { 
				add_mil_power = -200
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = grievance_trade
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = lenient_ruling
				}
				add_country_modifier = { 
					name = minor_trade_crisis
					duration = 2000
				}
			}
			else = { 
				add_country_modifier = { 
					name = minor_trade_crisis
					duration = 4000
				}
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = grievance_diplomatic
			}
			random_neighbor_country = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
				}
				ROOT = { 
					add_truce_with = PREV
				}
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = lenient_ruling
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						monthly_income = 50
					}
					add_treasury = -100
					random_neighbor_country = { 
						limit = { 
							has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						}
						add_treasury = 100
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						monthly_income = 25
					}
					add_treasury = -75
					random_neighbor_country = { 
						limit = { 
							has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						}
						add_treasury = 75
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						monthly_income = 10
					}
					add_treasury = -50
					random_neighbor_country = { 
						limit = { 
							has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						}
						add_treasury = 50
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						monthly_income = 5
					}
					add_treasury = -25
					random_neighbor_country = { 
						limit = { 
							has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						}
						add_treasury = 25
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						monthly_income = 2
					}
					add_treasury = -10
					random_neighbor_country = { 
						limit = { 
							has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						}
						add_treasury = 10
					}
				}
				else = { 
					add_treasury = -5
					random_neighbor_country = { 
						limit = { 
							has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						}
						add_treasury = 5
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						monthly_income = 50
					}
					add_treasury = -200
					random_neighbor_country = { 
						limit = { 
							has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						}
						add_treasury = 200
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						monthly_income = 25
					}
					add_treasury = -150
					random_neighbor_country = { 
						limit = { 
							has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						}
						add_treasury = 150
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						monthly_income = 10
					}
					add_treasury = -100
					random_neighbor_country = { 
						limit = { 
							has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						}
						add_treasury = 100
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						monthly_income = 5
					}
					add_treasury = -50
					random_neighbor_country = { 
						limit = { 
							has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						}
						add_treasury = 50
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						monthly_income = 2
					}
					add_treasury = -25
					random_neighbor_country = { 
						limit = { 
							has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						}
						add_treasury = 25
					}
				}
				else = { 
					add_treasury = -10
					random_neighbor_country = { 
						limit = { 
							has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
						}
						add_treasury = 10
					}
				}
			}
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = lenient_ruling
			}
			add_prestige = -5
		}
		else = { 
			add_prestige = -10
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.510.optb
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 50
		}
		add_legitimacy = -10
		add_devotion = -10
		add_republican_tradition = -10
		random_neighbor_country = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
			}
			add_casus_belli = { 
				type = cb_insult
				months = 24
				target = ROOT
			}
		}
	}
	after = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			random_neighbor_country = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = aggrieved_party
				}
				clr_country_flag = aggrieved_party
				clr_country_flag = grievance_diplomatic
				clr_country_flag = grievance_military
				clr_country_flag = grievance_trade
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = arbitration_bribe
				value = 0
			}
			clr_country_flag = grievance_diplomatic
			clr_country_flag = grievance_military
			clr_country_flag = grievance_trade
		}
	}
}
country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.511
	title = DG_Catholics.511.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.511.desc
	picture = catholic_papal_legate
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.511.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 50
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = grievance_military
			}
			add_mil_power = -50
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = grievance_trade
			}
			add_country_modifier = { 
				name = minor_trade_crisis
				duration = 1000
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = grievance_diplomatic
			}
			random_neighbor_country = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = grievance_compromise
				}
				ROOT = { 
					add_truce_with = PREV
				}
			}
		}
		add_opinion = { 
			who = PAP
			modifier = papacy_good
		}
		random_neighbor_country = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = grievance_compromise
			}
			add_opinion = { 
				who = ROOT
				modifier = grievance_resolved
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				clr_country_flag = grievance_compromise
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.511.optb
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 50
		}
		add_prestige = -5
		add_papal_influence = -5
	}
	after = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			random_neighbor_country = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = grievance_compromise
				}
				clr_country_flag = grievance_compromise
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = arbitration_bribe
				value = 0
			}
			clr_country_flag = aggrieved_party
			clr_country_flag = grievance_diplomatic
			clr_country_flag = grievance_military
			clr_country_flag = grievance_trade
		}
	}
}
province_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.512
	title = DG_Catholics.512.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.512.desc
	picture = orthodox_icon
	is_triggered_only = yes
	trigger = { 
		owner = { 
			OR = { 
				religion = catholic
				religion = avignonist
			}
		}
		religion = catholic
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = catholic_pilgrimage
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_province_modifier = religious_scandal_province
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.512.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 60
		}
		add_province_modifier = { 
			name = catholic_pilgrimage
			duration = 3650
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.512.optb
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 20
			modifier = { 
				NOT = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 30
						}
					}
				}
				factor = 2
			}
		}
		trigger = { 
			OR = { 
				has_province_modifier = effective_bishop
				owner = { 
					OR = { 
						advisor = inquisitor_CL
						advisor = theologian_CL
					}
				}
			}
		}
		add_province_modifier = { 
			name = religious_scandal_province
			duration = 730
		}
		owner = { 
			hidden_effect = { 
				every_owned_province = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = asx
								value = 0.001
							}
						}
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 5
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = atb
						value = 5
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 100.001
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							NOT = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = ata
										value = 0
									}
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 0
						}
					}
					set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_5
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.512.optc
		trigger = { 
			OR = { 
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = aai
						value = 500
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = aai
							value = 250
						}
					}
					has_province_modifier = greedy_bishop
				}
			}
		}
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 20
			modifier = { 
				num_of_loans = 1
				factor = 2
			}
		}
		owner = { 
			add_treasury = 25
			hidden_effect = { 
				every_owned_province = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = asx
								value = 0.001
							}
						}
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = -5
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = atb
						value = -5
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 100.001
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							NOT = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = ata
										value = 0
									}
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 0
						}
					}
					set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_-5
		}
		add_province_modifier = { 
			name = catholic_pilgrimage
			duration = 1825
		}
		add_province_modifier = { 
			name = religious_scandal_province
			duration = 1825
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			change_variable = { 
				which = aai
				value = -25
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = aai
								value = 1.0
							}
						}
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = aai
					value = 1.0
				}
			}
			set_province_flag = POP_ChangedWealth
		}
	}
}
country_event = { 
	id = DG_Catholics.513
	title = DG_Catholics.513.title
	desc = DG_Catholics.513.desc
	picture = catholic_burning_at_stake
	goto = auto_da_fe
	is_triggered_only = yes
	trigger = { 
		has_country_modifier = evangel_cm
		any_owned_province = { 
			has_owner_religion = yes
			AND = { 
				check_variable = { 
					which = asx
					value = 25
				}
			}
		}
	}
	immediate = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			random_owned_province = { 
				limit = { 
					has_owner_religion = yes
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asx
							value = 25
						}
					}
				}
				save_event_target_as = auto_da_fe
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.513.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 50
			modifier = { 
				NOT = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 30
						}
					}
				}
				factor = 2
			}
		}
		event_target:auto_da_fe = { 
			add_unrest = 10
			hidden_effect = { 
				set_variable = { 
					which = arn
					value = 10
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						always = yes
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = atc
									value = 0.001
								}
							}
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = ath
										value = 0.001
									}
								}
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = aro
								which = asx
							}
							change_variable = { 
								which = aro
								which = arn
							}
							if = { 
								limit = { 
									AND = { 
										check_variable = { 
											which = aro
											which = ath
										}
									}
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = arn
									which = ath
								}
								subtract_variable = { 
									which = arn
									which = asx
								}
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = aro
								value = 0
							}
						}
						else_if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = asx
										value = 0.001
									}
								}
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = arn
								value = 0
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = arn
								which = asx
							}
						}
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = asx
					which = arn
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = asz
					which = arn
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = asx
					value = 0.1
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = asx
					value = 10
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = asz
					value = 0.1
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = asz
					value = 10
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = asx
								value = 100
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = asx
						value = 100
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = asx
									value = 0
								}
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = asx
						value = 0
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = arn
					value = 0
				}
				set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
			}
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_owned_province = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asx
							value = 0.001
						}
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = ata
					value = 5
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = atb
					value = 5
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = ata
								value = 100.001
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 100
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 0
								}
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 0
					}
				}
				set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_5
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Catholics.513.optb
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 50
			modifier = { 
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 70
					}
				}
				factor = 2
			}
		}
		event_target:auto_da_fe = { 
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = religious_scandal_province
				duration = 3650
			}
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_owned_province = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asx
							value = 0.001
						}
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = ata
					value = -5
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = atb
					value = -5
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = ata
								value = 100.001
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 100
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 0
								}
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 0
					}
				}
				set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_-5
	}
